{"tid":961914,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「國民初戀」24歲秀智圓臉現身腫一圈 網友都驚呆了","createTime":"2018-12-30T13:02:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-31T02:54:57.000Z","uid":9573,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2872180e0b20ec624d7e1c688f22a42725d20870","tid":961914,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T13:02:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-12-24/656/20181224002582.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-12-24%2F656%2F20181224002582.jpg&h=0f611f07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n秀智有「國民初戀」稱號。<br />\n<br />\n24歲南韓女星秀智因外表清純有「國民初戀」稱號，影視歌三棲的她，出道以來人氣居高不下，不過近日她出席運動品牌滑動時，穿著白色羽絨長外套全身包緊緊，臉看上去圓了不少，似乎有些發福，但因為高顏值，讓她變胖還是看起來很美，意外成為討論焦點。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-12-24/656/20181224002584.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-12-24%2F656%2F20181224002584.jpg&h=c90e1680&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images.weserv.nl/?url=cms%2Dbucket%2Enosdn%2E127%2Enet%2F2018%2F11%2F28%2F05fb4ddbbf7e49679a4c1e5ca0b8ed75%2Ejpeg&amp;w=680&amp;output=jpg&amp;q=80&amp;errorredirect=cms%2Dbucket%2Enosdn%2E127%2Enet%2F2018%2F11%2F28%2F05fb4ddbbf7e49679a4c1e5ca0b8ed75%2Ejpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.weserv.nl%2F%3Furl%3Dcms%252Dbucket%252Enosdn%252E127%252Enet%252F2018%252F11%252F28%252F05fb4ddbbf7e49679a4c1e5ca0b8ed75%252Ejpeg%26w%3D680%26output%3Djpg%26q%3D80%26errorredirect%3Dcms%252Dbucket%252Enosdn%252E127%252Enet%252F2018%252F11%252F28%252F05fb4ddbbf7e49679a4c1e5ca0b8ed75%252Ejpeg&h=6a054f52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n秀智臉圓一圈仍被讚美。<br />\n<br />\n秀智帶著招牌甜美笑容現身，但臉蛋圓潤不少，加上穿著厚重衣服，顯得腫了一圈，不過顏值還是很高的她，看起來更童顏，被韓媒以「2倍的美麗」、「清純外貌」形容，粉絲也力挺應該是照片角度不對，「我老婆胖了也好看」、「臉圓更年輕」、「人家胖著玩玩別太在意，過沒多久就瘦回來了」。"},{"pid":"efd0f9362d5d37f3d26dc4698bdc02aca6d950ef","tid":961914,"uid":97179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T13:12:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2bb393e953cd2883df2b4d6fab994f2d8a7e2a9","tid":961914,"uid":4562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T13:14:21.000Z","msg":"渣古<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7720d8f85ffb3cd909ea55ca9626d713e84f8c5","tid":961914,"uid":76098,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T13:15:22.000Z","msg":"秀智+joy 雙飛 = 馬上風"},{"pid":"6f3c31944d1ac16787dba493d5b7c3f33f85e017","tid":961914,"uid":188406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T13:37:01.000Z","msg":"過氣"},{"pid":"1e84469ff1437a2b9e684a81e027b12781afacf9","tid":961914,"uid":815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T14:55:05.000Z","msg":"正皮俾配圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92d35bd05ff335d7fc455b96422428ebd6844e93","tid":961914,"uid":27616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T15:02:32.000Z","msg":"一樣咁正<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81a881de03b1e25b6292fa219d624552fb520d02","tid":961914,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T15:03:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cc3c52a27d9f5457db04b8747f9ed980a6f899e","tid":961914,"uid":23087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T15:06:46.000Z","msg":"有變咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85073c6d4cda3a5e0b0261264d32beb81e5eb0a3","tid":961914,"uid":54000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T15:08:12.000Z","msg":"屌，咁都有渣古<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e85c014e470f03c744a98c0d01a44384